# Tooltip — Visual Spec

## CSS classes

- `.acko-tooltip-trigger` — inline-flex
- `.acko-tooltip` — fixed, pointer-events-none, z-tooltip, background, color, font-caption, padding, radius-xl
- `.acko-tooltip-arrow` — CSS triangle var(--scale-6), positioned per side
- Enter animations per side: top/bottom/left/right with translate
- Animation: 150ms var(--ease-out-quad)
